<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Astra Dashboard</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0f111a; color: #ffffff; }
        .glass-panel { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen items-center justify-center p-6">
    <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-2xl max-w-2xl w-full">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Olá, <%= username %>!</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Você logou com sucesso. Aqui você poderá gerenciar seus servidores.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-black/30 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
            <p>Conexão ativa.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>